‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ tssconfig.json
``` */}

### Top-level Folders

| Folder                 | Description                          |
| ---------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| `src/mastra`           | Core application folder              |
| `src/mastra/agents`    | Agent configurations and definitions |
| `src/mastra/tools`     | Custom tool definitions              |
| `src/mastra/workflows` | Workflow definitions                 |

### Top-level Files

